replies.bodyText:
I think it's good. Come to think of it, perhaps also put in the Math.max(1, ...) trick in doMergeImages as well. E.g. do
int w = Math.max(1, Math.max(image1.getWidth(null), x + image2.getWidth(null)));
int h = Math.max(1, Math.max(image1.getHeight(null), y + image2.getHeight(null)));
Sorry for not catching this one earlier.
